(11, 66, 2, 'Girafarig', '[C][C] Tail Bite : 10+\r\nFlip a coin. If heads, this attack does 10 damage plus 20 more damage; if tails, this attack does 10 damage.\r\n\r\n[P][P] Psychic : 10+\r\nDoes 10 damage plus 10 more damage for each Energy card attached to the Defending Pokémon.', NULL),
