(13, 41, 2, 'Clefable', 'Poké-Power : Moonlight\r\nOnce during your turn (before your attack), you may put a card from you hand back on your deck. If you do, search your deck for a basic Energy card, show it to your opponent, and put it into your hand. Shuffle your deck afterward. This power can’t be used if Clefable is affected by a Special Condition.\r\n\r\n[C][C] Doubleslap : 20×\r\nFlip 2 coins. This attack does 20 times the number of heads.', NULL),
