(15, 79, 2, 'Murkrow', '[D] Evil Eye :\r\nChoose 1 of your opponent’s Pokémon. Put a damage counter on that Pokémon.\r\n\r\n[C][C] Blindside :\r\nChoose 1 of your opponent’s Pokémon that has a damage counter on it. This attack does 20 damage to that Pokémon. Don’t apply Weakness and Resistance.', NULL),
