(15, 81, 2, 'Nidoran ♀', '[C] Call for Family :\r\nSearch you deck for a Basic Pokémon card named Nidoran ♂ or Nidoran ♀ and put it onto your Bench. Shuffle your deck afterward. (You can’t use this attack if your Bench is full.)\r\n\r\n[G] Scratch : 10', NULL),
