(19, 5, 2, 'Team Aqua''s Sharpedo', '[C][C] Rage : 10+\r\nDoes 10 damage plus 10 more damage for each damage counter on Team Aqua’s Sharpedo.\r\n\r\n[W][W][C] Aqua Slash : 60\r\nTeam Aqua’s Sharpedo can’t attack during your next turn.', NULL),
