(23, 106, 2, 'Latios Star', '[C] Miraculous Light : 10\r\nRemove 1 damage counter and all special Conditions from Latios Star.\r\n\r\n[G][L][P] Shining Star : 50+\r\nIf the Defending Pokémon is a Stage 2 Evolved Pokémon, discard all Energy cards attached to Latios Star and this attack does 50 damage plus 100 more damage.', NULL),
