(34, 70, 2, 'Unown O', 'Poké-Power : One\r\nOnce during your turn (before your attack), if you have Unown O, Unown N, and Unown E on your Bench and you have 1 card left in your hand, you may draw cards until you have 7 cards in your hand.\r\n\r\n[C] Hidden Power : 10\r\nFlip a coin. If heads, the Defending Pokémon is now Asleep.', NULL),
(34, 71, 2, 'Unown X', 'Poké-Power : X-Ray\r\nOnce during your turn (before your attack), if you have Unown X on your Bench, you may look at the top card of your opponent''s deck and put it back on top of his or her deck.\r\n\r\n[C] Hidden Power : 10\r\nFlip a coin. If heads, the Defending Pokémon is now Paralyzed.', NULL),
(34, 72, 2, 'Unown Z', 'Poké-Power: Zero\r\nOnce during your turn (before your attack), if Unown Z is on your Bench and you have no cards in you deck, you may discard all cards attached to Unown Z and put Unown Z on top of your deck.\r\n\r\n[P][C] Hidden Power :\r\nRemove as many damage counters as you like from each Unown you have in play. Put that many damage counters on the Defending Pokémon.', NULL),
