(68, 83, 2, 'Togekiss-EX', 'Pokémon-EX rule : When a Pokémon-EX has been Knocked Out, your opponent takes 2 Prize cards.\r\n\r\n[Y] Mighty Wind : 20\r\nYou may attach an Energy card from your hand to 1 of your Benched Pokémon.\r\n\r\n[Y][C][C][C] Hurricane Wing : 50×\r\nFlip 4 coins. This attack does 50 damage times the number of heads.', NULL),
