(68, 97, 2, 'Bursting Balloon', 'Attach a Pokémon Tool to 1 of your Pokémon that doesn’t already have a Pokémon Tool attached to it.\r\n\r\nIf this card is attached to 1 of your Pokémon, discard it at the end of your opponent’s turn.\r\n\r\nIf the Pokémon this card is attached to is your Active Pokémon and is damaged by an opponent’s attack (even if that Pokémon is Knocked Out), put 6 damage counters on the Attacking Pokémon.', NULL),
(68, 98, 2, 'Delinquent', 'You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn (before your attack).\r\n\r\nDiscard any Stadium card in play. If you do, your opponent discards 3 cards from his or her hand.', NULL),
(68, 99, 2, 'Fighting Fury Belt', 'Attach a Pokémon Tool to 1 of your Pokémon that doesn’t already have a Pokémon Tool attached to it.\r\n\r\nThe Basic Pokémon this card is attached to gets +40 HP and its attacks do 10 more damage to your opponent’s Active Pokémon (before applying Weakness and Resistance).', NULL),
