(71, 66, 2, 'Yveltal BREAK', 'BREAK Evolution Rule : Yveltal BREAK retains the attacks, Abilities, Weakness, Resistance, and Retreat Cost of its previous Evolution.\r\n\r\n[D][D][D] Baleful Night : 120\r\nThis attack does 30 damage to each of your opponent’s Benched Pokémon that has any damage counters on it. (Don’t apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)', NULL),
