(71, 68, 2, 'M Steelix-EX', 'Mega Evolution rule : When 1 of your Pokémon becomes a Mega Evolution Pokémon, your turn ends.\r\n\r\nPokémon-EX rule : When a Pokémon-EX has been Knocked Out, your opponent takes 2 Prize cards.\r\n\r\n[M][C][C][C][C] Canyon Axe : 160\r\nThis attack does 10 damage to each of your opponent’s Benched Pokémon. (Don’t apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)', NULL),
