(5006, 186, 2, 'Magearna', '[C] Entertain :\r\nHeal 40 damage from 1 of your Benched Pokémon.\r\n\r\n[M] Prismatic Wave : 20×\r\nThis attack does 20 damage times the number of different types of Pokémon your opponent’s Bench.', 'Prismatic Wave'),
(5006, 187, 2, 'Celebi', '[C] Time Call :\r\nFlip a coin. If heads, search your deck for a card that evolves from 1 of your Pokémon and put it onto that Pokémon. (This counts as evolving that Pokémon.) Shuffle your deck afterward.\r\n\r\n[G] Leech Seed : 10\r\nHeal 10 damage from this Pokémon.', 'Time Call'),
