(74, 131, 2, 'Turtonator-GX', 'Pokémon-GX rule : When your Pokémon-GX is Knocked Out, your opponent takes 2 Prize cards.\r\n\r\n[C][C] Shell Trap : 20\r\nDuring your opponent’s next turn, if this Pokémon is damaged by an attack (even if this Pokémon is Knocked Out), put 8 damage counters on the Attacking Pokémon.\r\n\r\n[R][R][C] Bright Flame : 160\r\nDiscard 2 [R] Energy from this Pokémon.\r\n\r\n[R] Nitro Tank GX :\r\nAttach 5 [R] Energy cards from your discard pile to your Pokémon in any way you like. (You can’t use more than 1 GX attack in a game.)', NULL),
(74, 132, 2, 'Alolan Ninetales-GX', 'Pokémon-GX rule : When your Pokémon-GX is Knocked Out, your opponent takes 2 Prize cards.\r\n\r\n[C][C] Ice Blade :\r\nThis attack does 50 damage to 1 of your opponent’s Pokémon. (Don’t apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon).\r\n\r\n[W][W][C] Blizzard Edge : 160\r\nDiscard 2 Energy from this Pokémon.\r\n\r\n[C][C] Ice Path GX :\r\nMove all damage counters from this Pokémon to your opponent’s Active Pokémon. (You can’t use more than 1 GX attack in a game.)', NULL),
(74, 133, 2, 'Wishiwashi-GX', 'Pokémon-GX rule : When your Pokémon-GX is Knocked Out, your opponent takes 2 Prize cards.\r\n\r\n[W] Water Gun : 20\r\n\r\n[W][W][W][C][C] Torrential Vortex : 120\r\nDiscard a Special Energy from your opponent’s Active Pokémon.\r\n\r\n[W][W][W][C][C] Blue Surge GX : 220\r\nMove all Energy from this Pokémon to your Benched Pokémon in any way you like. (You can’t use more than 1 GX attack in a game.)', NULL),
